title: Legal Aspects of Patient Care by Professor R.K.Sharma
description:
Legal Aspects of Patient Care by Professor R.K.Sharma (complete with front and back cover as a single pdf file)

An excellent book for doctors and medicolegal professionals. Many laws relating to medicine are given as well as several actual cases to illustrate important points.
This is the most complete version available till date. It includes front and back cover in full cover.
An absolute must for all.
